beer.beer_name: KAIJU! Demon Cleaner West Coast IPA (Mutation Program #005)
beer.beer_description:
son than because we like it. Demon Cleaner is a mad representation of an American West Coast IPA featuring Strata Hops.
Strata brings all your favourite hop buzzwords together in one hop, tropical, dank, coconut etc. Nelson provides more tropical character particularly passionfruit and white-wine characters. Malt is super lean and  (in traditional KAIJU! Fashion) yeast esters are kept to a minimum to let the hops shine.
